## Attribution / 致谢

kpop-design-system 的安装器架构、检测算法、防误装机制衍生自姊妹项目
**suanfish-design-system** (https://github.com/SuanFishXYY/suanfish-design-system).

The installer architecture, CLI detection algorithm, and anti-mis-install guard
of kpop-design-system are derived from sister project
**suanfish-design-system** (https://github.com/SuanFishXYY/suanfish-design-system).

两个项目共享治理体系：Bug #1-#9 治理史、虚拟环境沙箱验证、虚拟机器装机规约。
Both projects share governance lineage: Bug #1-#9 remediation history,
virtual sandbox verification, virgin-machine install conventions.

KPOP idol personality data is curated original work by 算鱼工作室.
The 97 idol agent profiles, vote weights, attitude→UI mappings are original
creative contributions and licensed under MIT alongside the codebase.